<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.8">
<l>mañcuyar māma titīṇṭa nīṇṭa māliruñ cōlai maṇāḷar vanteṉ</l>
<l>neñcuḷḷuṅ kaṇṇuḷ ḷumniṉ ṟunīṅkār nīrmalai yārkol niṉaikka māṭṭēṉ</l>
<l>mañcuyar poṉma laimē leḻunta māmukil pōṉṟu ḷarvan tukāṇīr</l>
<l>añciṟaip puḷḷu moṉṟē ṟivantā raccō voruva raḻaki yavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The groom of Māliruñcōlai, which reaches up</l>
<l rend="indent">to touch the great moon where mist rises,</l>
<l>Having come into my heart and into [my] eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">abiding [there], does not depart. Is he the one from Nīrmalai?</l>
<l>I cannot understand [it]. He is like a dark cloud</l>
<l rend="indent">risen on a gold mountain where mist rises.</l>
<l>Come see! And he came riding on a fine, winged bird.</l>
<l rend="indent">Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
